{"tid":2223882,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"VMware和NVIDIA推出新一代混合雲架構","createTime":"2020-09-30T06:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T12:58:21.000Z","uid":81914,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f553df89c6f999e435085830c901e1b273a48e6c","tid":2223882,"uid":81914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"超過30萬VMware客戶將受惠於可以統一管理NVIDIA AI軟體及所有應用，同時具有安全性和NVIDIA BlueField-2 DPU加速功能<br />\n在VMworld 2020大會上，VMware和NVIDIA宣佈展開進一步合作，推出針對AI的端到端企業平台以及採用NVIDIA&reg;&nbsp;&nbsp;DPU、針對資料中心、雲端和邊緣的全新架構，支援現有及新一代的應用。<br />\n透過此次合作，NVIDIA NGCTM中心上的豐富AI軟體將被整合至VMware vSphere、VMware Cloud Foundation和VMware Tanzu中，將有助於加速AI部署，支援企業擴展現有的AI基礎架構，通過單一操作來管理所有應用程式，並在數據留存之處部署跨資料中心、雲端和邊緣的AI就緒基礎架構。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/news/news-01/86033/vmware和nvidia推出新一代混合雲架構，讓企業享有ai運算/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-01%2F86033%2Fvmware%E5%92%8Cnvidia%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E6%B7%B7%E5%90%88%E9%9B%B2%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%93%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E4%BA%AB%E6%9C%89ai%E9%81%8B%E7%AE%97%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=987fd894\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/news/news-01/86033/vmware和nvidia推出新一代混合雲架構，讓企業享有ai運算/</a>"},{"pid":"f045a957e6308ed2c9ebf5e514d0a0f8980d1c95","tid":2223882,"uid":81914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"加埋下星期Gtc 大把新技術公佈   今晚一定爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj